---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="ZERO OS — Your AI. Your keys. Your trades.">

<!-- STICKY NAV -->
<nav class="nav" id="site-nav">
  <a href="#top" class="nav-logo"><span class="pg">◇</span> ZERO OS</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#how" class="nav-link">How it works</a>
    <a href="/thesis" class="nav-link">Thesis</a>
    <a href="#access" class="nav-cta">Request Access</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="page" id="top">

  <!-- S1: HERO -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="boot-seq">
      <pre class="bl" data-text="ZERO OS v0.1 .................... BOOT"></pre>
      <pre class="bl" data-text="ENVY MATRIX .................... ACTIVE"></pre>
      <pre class="bl" data-text="PORTFOLIO ENGINE ............... SELF-CUSTODIAL"></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <pre class="logo-art">████████╗ ███████╗ ██████╗   ██████╗
╚══███╔═╝ ██╔════╝ ██╔══██╗ ██╔═══██╗
  ███╔╝   █████╗   ██████╔╝ ██║   ██║
 ███╔╝    ██╔══╝   ██╔══██╗ ██║   ██║
████████╗ ███████╗ ██║  ██║ ╚██████╔╝
╚═══════╝ ╚══════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝  ╚═════╝</pre>
      <div class="crt-scan"></div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">Your AI.<br>Your keys.<br>Your trades.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">ZERO is the self-custodial OS for AI trading agents. Install locally. Set your rules. Your agent handles the rest — 24/7, on your machine.</p>
    <p class="hero-engines">Works with <span class="pg">Claude</span> · <span class="pg">OpenClaw</span> · <span class="pg">Perplexity Computer</span> · any agent engine</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#access" class="btn-primary">Request Early Access →</a>
      <a href="/thesis" class="btn-ghost">Read the thesis →</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- S2: PROOF -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="proof">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">MONTE CARLO BACKTEST</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">14 out of 15 coins profitable.<br>Even in the worst-case scenario.</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub dim reveal-child">Monte Carlo simulation across 15 assets. These aren't cherry-picked runs — even the 5th percentile (worst 5% of outcomes) stays profitable.</p>
    <div class="tbl-wrap reveal-child">
      <table class="tbl">
        <thead>
          <tr><th class="c-coin">COIN</th><th>RETURN</th><th>WIN RATE</th><th>MAX DD</th><th class="hm">p5 RETURN*</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">BTC</td><td class="pos">+52.2%</td><td>50.9%</td><td class="dd">-14.9%</td><td class="pos hm">+35.3%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">ETH</td><td class="pos">+77.4%</td><td>39.8%</td><td class="dd">-28.3%</td><td class="pos hm">+42.0%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">SOL</td><td class="pos">+86.5%</td><td>43.4%</td><td class="dd">-16.0%</td><td class="pos hm">+50.4%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">ARB</td><td class="pos">+95.8%</td><td>37.1%</td><td class="dd">-23.1%</td><td class="pos hm">+45.6%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">CRV</td><td class="pos">+127.0%</td><td>34.7%</td><td class="dd-hot">-31.5%</td><td class="pos hm">+43.7%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">KPEPE</td><td class="pos">+256.1%</td><td>37.7%</td><td class="dd">-20.4%</td><td class="pos hm">+165.0%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">KBONK</td><td class="pos">+224.6%</td><td>32.6%</td><td class="dd-hot">-29.2%</td><td class="pos hm">+143.2%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">TRX</td><td class="pos">+59.4%</td><td class="best-wr">61.3%</td><td class="dd-safe">-8.3%</td><td class="pos hm">+47.8%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">DOGE</td><td class="pos">+47.6%</td><td>38.2%</td><td class="dd">-19.7%</td><td class="pos hm">+20.1%</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="c-coin">KSHIB</td><td class="pos">+117.7%</td><td>43.0%</td><td class="dd">-17.8%</td><td class="pos hm">+70.7%</td></tr>
          <tr class="row-neg"><td class="c-coin">PAXG</td><td class="neg">-5.1%</td><td>49.2%</td><td class="dd-safe">-11.3%</td><td class="neg hm">-14.1%</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="fnote dim reveal-child">* p5 = 5th percentile. 95% of outcomes were better than this number.<br>10,000 runs · 2023–2025 data · 0.1% fee + 0.05% slippage · <a href="/thesis" class="lnk">Full methodology →</a></p>
    <div class="stats reveal-child">
      <div class="stat tilt-card"><div class="stat-n pg" data-count-to="14" data-count-suffix="/15">0/15</div><div class="stat-l dim">coins profitable at median</div></div>
      <div class="stat tilt-card"><div class="stat-n amber" data-count-to="37" data-count-suffix="%">0%</div><div class="stat-l dim">avg win rate — wins 3–5× larger</div></div>
      <div class="stat tilt-card"><div class="stat-n ice">p5+</div><div class="stat-l dim">worst 5% of simulations still profit</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- S3: HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="how">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">HOW IT WORKS</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">Three minutes.<br>Then it runs forever.</h2>
    <div class="steps reveal-child">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n pg">01</div>
        <div class="step-title">INSTALL</div>
        <p class="step-d dim">One command. Runs on your machine. Your keys never leave your device. No cloud. No trust required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-conn"><span class="pg">· · ·</span></div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n pg">02</div>
        <div class="step-title">CONFIGURE</div>
        <p class="step-d dim">Set your risk limits. Choose your mode — observation to full autonomy. The agent handles exchange execution natively.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-conn"><span class="pg">· · ·</span></div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-n pg">03</div>
        <div class="step-title">TRADE</div>
        <p class="step-d dim">Your agent detects market conditions, manages your portfolio, executes trades, and rebalances — 24/7, on your terms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- S4: AGENT ENGINES (NEW) -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="engines">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">AGENT INFRASTRUCTURE</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">Bring your own brain.<br>We provide the body.</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub dim reveal-child">ZERO doesn't lock you into one AI. It's the execution layer — self-custodial trading infrastructure that works with any agent engine. You choose the intelligence. ZERO handles keys, execution, risk, and settlement.</p>
    <div class="engines reveal-child">
      <div class="eng"><span class="eng-n pg">Claude</span><span class="eng-l dim">Anthropic</span></div>
      <div class="eng"><span class="eng-n pg">OpenClaw</span><span class="eng-l dim">Agentic OS</span></div>
      <div class="eng"><span class="eng-n pg">Perplexity</span><span class="eng-l dim">Computer</span></div>
      <div class="eng"><span class="eng-n pg">GPT</span><span class="eng-l dim">OpenAI</span></div>
      <div class="eng"><span class="eng-n pg">Gemini</span><span class="eng-l dim">Google</span></div>
      <div class="eng eng-plus"><span class="eng-n dim">+ Your model</span><span class="eng-l dim">Any engine</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="arch-flow reveal-child">
      <span class="dim">[Your AI Engine]</span>
      <span class="pg"> → </span>
      <span class="arch-zero">[ZERO OS]</span>
      <span class="pg"> → </span>
      <span class="dim">[Trades]</span>
    </div>
    <p class="engines-kicker reveal-child">The AI landscape changes every month. Your trading infrastructure shouldn't.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- S5: AUTONOMY MODES -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="modes">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">MODES</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">You choose the level of autonomy.</h2>
    <div class="modes reveal-child">
      <div class="mode" style="--mo:0.4">
        <div class="mode-bar" style="background:var(--tx2)"></div>
        <div class="mode-body">
          <div class="mode-hd"><span class="mode-n dim">OBSERVE</span><span class="mode-tag">FREE</span></div>
          <p class="mode-d dim">Watch the agent think. See signals, portfolio analysis, regime shifts. No trades executed. Training wheels on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mode" style="--mo:0.6">
        <div class="mode-bar" style="background:var(--amber)"></div>
        <div class="mode-body">
          <div class="mode-hd"><span class="mode-n amber">SIGNAL</span><span class="mode-tag">COMPUTE</span></div>
          <p class="mode-d dim">Agent generates buy/sell signals with reasoning. You execute manually. Full control, informed decisions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mode" style="--mo:0.8">
        <div class="mode-bar" style="background:var(--ice)"></div>
        <div class="mode-body">
          <div class="mode-hd"><span class="mode-n ice">SEMI-AUTO</span><span class="mode-tag">COMPUTE</span></div>
          <p class="mode-d dim">Agent prepares trades and notifies you. One tap to approve. Kill switch always active.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mode" style="--mo:1.0">
        <div class="mode-bar pg-bar"></div>
        <div class="mode-body">
          <div class="mode-hd"><span class="mode-n pg">FULL AUTO</span><span class="mode-tag pg">FULL AUTONOMY</span></div>
          <p class="mode-d dim">Portfolio management, rebalancing, position sizing — 24/7, within your risk parameters.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- S6: THE INTELLIGENCE + MATRIX -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="intelligence">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">THE INTELLIGENCE</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">Your agent sees what others can't.</h2>
    <div class="intel-copy reveal-child">
      <p class="dim">Every trading bot uses the same indicators — RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands. They all assume the market behaves the same way every day. It doesn't.</p>
      <p class="dim" style="margin-top:0.75rem">Markets shift between states: trending, choppy, chaotic, calm. A signal that works in one state is a trap in another. ZERO detects the state first. Then decides if the signal matters.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="comparison reveal-child">
      <div class="cmp-row">
        <span class="cmp-old dim">RSI says overbought</span>
        <span class="cmp-arr dim">→</span>
        <span class="cmp-new pg">We know if RSI even applies right now.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cmp-row">
        <span class="cmp-old dim">MACD shows a crossover</span>
        <span class="cmp-arr dim">→</span>
        <span class="cmp-new pg">We tell you if that crossover is meaningful or a trap.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="matrix-block reveal-child">
      <div class="matrix-hd">
        <span class="sec-label pg" style="margin-bottom:0">LIVE REGIME DETECTION</span>
        <span class="mstatus" id="matrix-status">scanning</span>
      </div>
      <div class="matrix-wrap"><canvas id="matrix-canvas"></canvas></div>
    </div>
    <div class="gauges reveal-child">
      <div class="gauge">
        <span class="gauge-lbl">TREND STRENGTH <span class="dim">(Hurst Exponent)</span></span>
        <div class="g-track"><div class="g-fill" id="rv-hurst"></div><div class="g-mark" id="rv-hurst-marker"></div></div>
        <span class="g-val" id="rv-hurst-val">0.50</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gauge">
        <span class="gauge-lbl">PATTERN STABILITY <span class="dim">(DFA)</span></span>
        <div class="g-track"><div class="g-fill" id="rv-dfa"></div><div class="g-mark" id="rv-dfa-marker"></div></div>
        <span class="g-val" id="rv-dfa-val">0.50</span>
      </div>
      <div class="gauge">
        <span class="gauge-lbl">CHAOS LEVEL <span class="dim">(Lyapunov)</span></span>
        <div class="g-track"><div class="g-fill g-fill-chaos" id="rv-lyap"></div><div class="g-mark" id="rv-lyap-marker"></div></div>
        <span class="g-val" id="rv-lyap-val">0.30</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="regime-out reveal-child">
      <div class="r-badge" id="rv-badge">SCANNING</div>
      <p class="r-verdict" id="rv-verdict">Your MACD crossover is → <span class="dim">ANALYZING</span></p>
    </div>
    <p class="thesis-lnk dim reveal-child">Want the math? <a href="/thesis" class="lnk">Read the full thesis →</a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- S7: SELF-CUSTODIAL -->
  <section class="sec reveal" id="security">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">SELF-CUSTODIAL</p>
    <h2 class="sec-h2 reveal-child">Your keys never leave your machine.</h2>
    <ul class="custody reveal-child">
      <li><span class="pg">✓</span> Keys managed locally by the agent, encrypted at rest</li>
      <li><span class="pg">✓</span> All trades execute from your device</li>
      <li><span class="pg">✓</span> Kill switch — pause everything instantly</li>
      <li><span class="pg">✓</span> Built-in position limits and daily loss caps</li>
      <li><span class="pg">✓</span> No cloud dependency — runs offline if needed</li>
    </ul>
    <pre class="kill-demo reveal-child">$ zero-os --kill
<span class="pg">></span> All positions frozen. No new trades.
<span class="pg">></span> Resume with: zero-os --resume</pre>
  </section>

  <!-- S8: CTA -->
  <section class="sec cta-sec reveal" id="access">
    <p class="sec-label reveal-child">EARLY ACCESS</p>
    <p class="cta-ctx dim reveal-child">Seeking design partners — funds, desks, and serious traders who want first access.</p>
    <div class="term-cta reveal-child">
      <div class="term-hd">
        <span class="dim">zero-os</span>
        <span class="t-dots"><span class="d-r"></span><span class="d-a"></span><span class="d-g"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="term-bd">
        <p class="tl dim">$ zero-os --status</p>
        <p class="tl"><span class="pg">&gt;</span> Regime detection: <span class="pg">BUILT</span></p>
        <p class="tl"><span class="pg">&gt;</span> Self-custodial execution: <span class="pg">READY</span></p>
        <p class="tl"><span class="pg">&gt;</span> Onboarding design partners now.</p>
        <p class="tl dim" style="margin-top:0.5rem">$ zero-os request_access<span class="tcursor"></span></p>
        <form class="tform" id="access-form">
          <div class="t-row"><span class="pg">email:</span><input type="email" id="access-email" class="t-input" placeholder="you@fund.com" required></div>
          <button type="submit" class="t-submit">SUBMIT ↵</button>
        </form>
        <p id="term-confirm" style="display:none" class="tl"><span class="pg">✓ ACCESS_REQUEST_QUEUED</span><br><span class="dim">ref: ZOS-<span id="req-id">0000</span> — we'll be in touch.</span></p>
        <p id="term-error" style="display:none" class="tl"><span class="red">✗ CONNECTION_ERROR</span><br><span class="dim">Try again or email <a href="mailto:degenie@getzero.dev" class="lnk">degenie@getzero.dev</a>.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<footer class="footer">
  <span><span class="pg">◇</span> <span class="dim">ZERO OS</span></span>
  <span class="footer-r"><a href="/thesis" class="dim lnk">Thesis</a> · <a href="mailto:degenie@getzero.dev" class="dim lnk">degenie@getzero.dev</a></span>
</footer>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ═══ PALETTE OVERRIDE (spec v2) ═══ */
:root {
  --phosphor: #00FF41;
  --phosphor-glow: rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
  --amber: #ffb000;
  --ice: #00d4ff;
  --red: #ff4444;
  --text: #E0E0E0;
  --text-dim: #888888;
  --tx2: #888888;
  --tx3: #555555;
  --bg: #050505;
  --bg2: #0A0A0A;
  --bg3: #0D0D0D;
  --border: #1A1A1A;
  --font-head: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', 'SF Mono', monospace;
  --font-body: 'IBM Plex Mono', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
}

/* ═══ CRT OVERLAY ═══ */
body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.025) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.025) 4px);
  pointer-events: none; z-index: 100;
}
@media (max-width: 639px) { body::before { display: none; } }

/* ═══ NAV ═══ */
.nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 200;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
  background: transparent;
  border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
  transition: background 0.4s, border-color 0.4s, backdrop-filter 0.4s;
  font-family: var(--font-head);
}
.nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(5,5,5,0.88);
  border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
}
.nav-logo { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
.nav-link { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--tx2); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
.nav-link:hover { color: var(--text); }
.nav-cta {
  font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--phosphor); border: 1px solid var(--phosphor);
  padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem; text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.08); box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(0,255,65,0.1); }
@media (max-width: 639px) {
  .nav { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
  .nav-links { gap: 0.75rem; }
  .nav-link { display: none; }
}

/* ═══ PAGE ═══ */
.page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
@media (max-width: 639px) { .page { padding: 0 1rem; } }

/* ═══ HERO ═══ */
.hero { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.boot-seq { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.bl {
  font-family: var(--font-head);
  font-size: clamp(0.38rem, 2.2vw, 0.52rem);
  color: var(--tx2); margin: 0; line-height: 1.9;
  white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; min-height: 1.9em;
}
.bl .bcursor { color: var(--phosphor); animation: blink 0.6s step-end infinite; }

.logo-wrap { position: relative; margin-bottom: 2rem; overflow: hidden; }
.logo-art {
  font-family: var(--font-head);
  font-size: clamp(6px, calc((100vw - 40px) / 40), 21px);
  line-height: 1.15; color: var(--phosphor); white-space: pre; margin: 0;
  border: none; background: transparent;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: logoIn 0.6s ease 0.9s both, logoGlow 4s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite;
}
@keyframes logoIn {
  0% { opacity: 0; filter: brightness(5) blur(4px); }
  50% { opacity: 0.8; filter: brightness(1.5) blur(1px); }
  100% { opacity: 1; filter: brightness(1) blur(0); }
}
@keyframes logoGlow {
  0%,100% { text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,255,65,0.15); }
  50% { text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(0,255,65,0.3), 0 0 40px rgba(0,255,65,0.08); }
}
.crt-scan {
  position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px;
  background: var(--phosphor); opacity: 0.05;
  animation: scanDrop 3.5s linear infinite; pointer-events: none;
}
@keyframes scanDrop { 0% { top: 0; } 100% { top: 100%; } }

.hero-h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-head);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.08;
  color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.1s both;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 2vw, 1rem);
  color: var(--tx2); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 540px;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.3s both;
}
.hero-engines {
  font-family: var(--font-head);
  font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--tx3);
  letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.45s both;
}
.hero-cta {
  display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
  animation: fadeUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) 1.6s both;
}
@media (max-width: 639px) { .hero-cta { flex-direction: column; } .hero-cta a { text-align: center; } }
@keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(14px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

.btn-primary {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--phosphor);
  background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--phosphor);
  padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem; text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  transition: background 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}
.btn-primary::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%;
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0,255,65,0.08), transparent);
  animation: sweep 3s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes sweep { 0% { left:-100%; } 100% { left:100%; } }
.btn-primary:hover { background: rgba(0,255,65,0.08); box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,255,65,0.12); }
.btn-ghost {
  font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--tx2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
  text-decoration: none; transition: border-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
}
